        },
        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=Return your response in STRICT JSON format with these exact keys:\n1. \"intent\": Classify the message as 'Support', 'Sales', or 'Feedback'.\n2. \"urgency\": Classify as 'High', 'Medium', or 'Low'.\n3. \"html_report\": A string containing the full HTML KPI Dashboard.\n\nCRITICAL HTML RULES FOR THE AI:\n- You MUST use actual HTML tags (<h2>, <ul>, <li>, <table>, <tr>, <td>).\n- DO NOT strip the tags. \n- DO NOT use \\n for line breaks. \n- DO NOT use markdown format.\n\nUse this EXACT HTML template for the \"html_report\" value:\n<h2>Monthly KPI Dashboard - {{ $json.month }}</h2>\n<p><strong>Narrative Summary:</strong> [Write summary here]</p>\n<h3>Key Highlights</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>[Highlight 1]</li>\n  <li>[Highlight 2]</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Performance Data</h3>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\">\n  <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\"><th>Metric</th><th>Current Value</th><th>MoM Growth</th></tr>\n  <tr><td>Revenue</td><td>${{ $json.revenue }}</td><td>{{ $json.rev_growth }}</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Expenses</td><td>${{ $json.expenses }}</td><td>{{ $json.exp_growth }}</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Customers</td><td>{{ $json.customers }}</td><td>{{ $json.cust_growth }}</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Churn</td><td>{{ $json.churn }}</td><td>{{ $json.churn_growth }}</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>ARPU</td><td>${{ $json.arpu }}</td><td>{{ $json.arpu_growth }}</td></tr>\n</table>"
            }
          ]
        },
